                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing sponge iron from red mud negative carbon",
                    "一种赤泥负碳制备海绵铁的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing sponge iron from red mud negative carbon, which comprises the following steps: by taking hydrogen as a reducing agent and fluidizing gas, carrying out low-temperature fluidization solid-state reduction on iron oxide in the red mud to metal iron, and carrying out magnetic separation to obtain high-activity sponge iron with the metallization ratio of more than or equal to 90%; biomass fuel combustion is adopted to provide heat needed by the system, carbon-containing tail gas obtained after combustion is carbonized through red mud to remove carbon dioxide, and negative carbon emission of the system is achieved. A high-gas-speed grading fluidized bed internally provided with inert particle bed materials is adopted, drying, dewatering, scattering and conveying preheating of the red mud carbonized materials are achieved, and meanwhile the inert particle bed materials can effectively maintain the bed layer temperature to be stable; the energy utilization rate of the system is improved through heat exchange between cold air and hot carbon-containing tail gas and heat exchange between cold hydrogen and hot reduction materials. The method has the advantages of simple process equipment, simplicity and convenience in operation, low energy consumption, negative carbon emission and environmental friendliness, can realize large-scale clean and efficient preparation of high-activity sponge iron from red mud, and has good economic and social benefits."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种赤泥负碳制备海绵铁的方法，以氢气为还原剂和流化气，低温流态化固态还原赤泥中的氧化铁至金属铁，磁选得到高活性海绵铁，海绵铁的金属化率≥90％；采用生物质燃料燃烧提供系统所需热量，燃烧后的含碳尾气经赤泥碳化脱除二氧化碳，实现系统负碳排放；采用内置惰性颗粒床料的高气速分级流化床，实现对赤泥碳化料的干燥、脱水、打散和输送预热，同时惰性颗粒床料可以有效维持床层温度稳定；通过冷空气与热含碳尾气换热、冷氢气与热还原料换热，提高系统能量利用率。本发明工艺设备简单，操作简便，能耗低，负碳排放，环境友好，可以实现赤泥大规模清洁高效制备高活性海绵铁，具有良好的经济效益和社会效益。"
                }
